Colors are garish and dont mesh well with eachother to make it easier to just use the bucket tool and fill in the new colors

colors and what they correspond to
#e30064 -> Primary background color
#ff7811 -> Lighter background color
#ffc107 -> (more) Lighter background color
#921979 -> Darker background color
#44258c -> (more) Darker background color
#6dc927 -> Primary foreground color
#008c8c -> Darker foreground color
